<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" dir="ltr">
    <head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
	    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./mincss/styles.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./vendors/aos/dist/aos.css">
	    <title>WeMake</title>
    </head>
    <body>
    	<header class="global-header">
    		<nav class="container">
    			<div class="row align-center">
					<div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
						<h1><a href="/" title="WeMake">WEMAKE</a></h1>
					</div>
					<div class="col-lg-6">
						<ul class="menu">
							<li>
								<a href="/galerie" title="Galerie publique" class="menu__link">Galerie publique</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/connexion" title="Connexion"  class="menu__link menu__link--strong">Connexion</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/inscription" title="Inscription"  class="menu__link menu__link--strong">Inscription</a>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
    			</div>
    		</nav>
    	</header>
        <main>
            <section class="container introduction">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                        <h2 class="introduction__title">
                            Seul ou à plusieurs,<br> retouchez vos photos pour <br> leurs donner un nouveau style
                        </h2>
                        <p class="introduction__text">
                            WeMake est une plateforme de retouche d’images  collaborative permettant à ses utilisateurs de retoucher des images seul ou à plusieurs.
                            Les utilisateurs peuvent partager  leur projet et ainsi avoir un retour de la communauté.
                        </p>
                        <div class="introduction__btn">
                            <a href="/connexion" class="button button--blue" title="Créer un projet">Créer un projet</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                        <div class="introduction__image">
                            <img src="./images/demo.png" alt="Démonstration">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="container-fluid features">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2 class="features__title">.: Les fonctionnalités</h2>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 || feature" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-offset="150" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out" data-aos-duration="400">
                            <h3>De nombreux outils</h3>
                            <img src="./images/tools.svg" alt="De nombreux outils" class="feature__img">
                            <p class="feature__text">WeMake met à votre disposition tous les outils nécessaires pour la retouche d’images (filtres, texte...)</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 || feature" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-offset="150" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out" data-aos-duration="400" data-aos-delay="400">
                            <h3>Plateforme collaborative</h3>
                            <img src="./images/people.svg" alt="Plateforme collaborative" class="feature__img">
                            <p class="feature__text">Retouchez vos images en groupe dans des salles d’éditions allant jusqu’à 10 participants.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 || feature" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-offset="150" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out" data-aos-duration="400" data-aos-delay="800">
                            <h3>Partagez vos projets</h3>
                            <img src="./images/public.svg" alt="Partagez vos projets" class="feature__img">
                            <p class="feature__text">Partagez votre projet en un seul clic et obtenez des retours de la communauté WeMake.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="container-fluid registration">
                <p class="registration__text">Vous n’êtes pas encore inscrit ? <br /> Rejoignez maintenant la communauté.</p>
                <a href="/inscription" class="button button--blue" title="Je m'inscris">Je m'inscris</a>
                <div class="registration__overlay"></div>
            </section>
            <section class="container popular-projects">
                <h2 class="text-center popular-projects__title">.: Projets populaires</h2>
                <div class="row center">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 popular-projects__three" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-offset="150" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out" data-aos-duration="400">
                        <div>
                            <div class="popular-projects__three__image" style="background:url('../images/road.jpg')"></div>
                            <div class="popular-projects__three__box-infos">
                                <h4 class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__title"><a href="#">Retouche luminosité</a></h4>
                                <span class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__author">JeromeCrea</span>
                                <div class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__like">
                                    <span class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__like__counter">23</span>
                                    <input type="submit" class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__like__icon" value="">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 popular-projects__three" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-offset="150" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out" data-aos-duration="400">
                        <div>
                            <div class="popular-projects__three__image" style="background:url('../images/nature.jpg')"></div>
                            <div class="popular-projects__three__box-infos">
                                <h4 class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__title"><a href="#">Retouche contraste</a></h4>
                                <span class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__author">Simon57</span>
                                <div class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__like">
                                    <span class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__like__counter">17</span>
                                    <input type="submit" class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__like__icon" value="">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 popular-projects__three" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-offset="150" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out" data-aos-duration="400">
                        <div>
                            <div class="popular-projects__three__image" style="background:url('../images/road.jpg')"></div>
                            <div class="popular-projects__three__box-infos">
                                <h4 class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__title"><a href="#">Retouche luminosité</a></h4>
                                <span class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__author">JeromeCrea</span>
                                <div class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__like">
                                    <span class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__like__counter">15</span>
                                    <input type="submit" class="popular-projects__three__box-infos__like__icon" value="">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/galerie" title="Tous les projets" class="button button--blue margin-auto">Tous les projets</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <footer class="container-fluid footer">
            <a href="#" title="WeMake" class="footer__link">WeMake</a>
            <a href="#" title="Mentions légales" class="footer__link">Mentions légales</a>
            <a href="#" title="Nous contacter" class="footer__link">Nous contacter</a>
        </footer>
        <script src="/vendors/aos/dist/aos.js"></script>
        <script src="./minjs/script.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>
